Will YOU Press the Button? - Bacon For ALL ► http://bit.ly/1TdBci1

Think parenting is hard? This game PROVES it! One of YOU sent me an article about this new indie game (Who's Your Daddy?), where one person is a baby trying to kill itself, and the other person is a father trying to baby proof the apartment. I knew Steph and I had to give this one a try. Let's see if we can save one child's life.
